{
  "texts": [
    "We report ICL results with ChatGPT (GPT-3.5-turbo) or LLaMA-2-7B.",
    "Results and AnalysisWe first compare all the systems ( § 4.1), and then conduct ablation study on the training effect of each reward type ( § 4.2).",
    "We also analyze the effect of retrieval on the final model performance ( § 4.3), and the citation errors that we observe ( § 4.4).",
    "Lastly, we test our models' generalization capability on EXPERTQA that is unseen during training ( § 4.5).",
    "Main ResultsThe main results are summarized in Table 1.Training with fine-grained rewards greatly boosts performance."
  ]
}